# =============================================================================
# Urja Basket — Monorepo environment reference
# Each app has its own .env.example — copy to .env / .env.local per service.
# =============================================================================
#
#   server/.env.example   → Express API (port from PORT)
#   frontend/.env.example → Next.js storefront (port from PORT)
#   admin/.env.example    → Next.js admin console (port from PORT)
#
# Production deployment: AWS EC2 (PM2 + Nginx). API guide: server/DEPLOYMENT.md
#
# =============================================================================

# Quick production checklist (set per app on EC2):
#
# API service (server/):
#   PORT, CORS_ORIGIN, ADMIN_API_KEY, CLERK_*, RAZORPAY_*,
#   DB_HOST/DB_USER/DB_PASSWORD/DB_NAME (or MYSQL_URL for RDS)
#
# Storefront (frontend/):
#   PORT, NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY, CLERK_SECRET_KEY,
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID, NEXT_PUBLIC_ADMIN_URL
#
# Admin (admin/):
#   PORT, INTERNAL_API_URL, ADMIN_API_KEY, ADMIN_APP_PASSWORD, ADMIN_SESSION_SECRET
